Description: Starcraft data game set for the Stratagus engine
 Stargus can be used to play Starcraft from Blizzard Entertainment.
 .
 You need the original Starcraft CD to extract the game data files.
 .
 Stargus is developed together for Windows, Linux and Mac OS X.
